&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://mariusschulz.com/blog/control-flow-based-type-analysis-in-typescript&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Control Flow Based Type Analysis in TypeScript — Marius Schulz&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
